<p>Don't ask me why I put these here. I thought they would hold a purpose or something. And incase I see something interesting someone says, I might as well put it here to teach people a thing or two. Might have some from the wiki and some that are not. A few quotes might involve why some scips were created. A few of the quotes might be silly.</p>


